      "content": "i dont want to talk to a counselor. they just say the same stuff. \"it gets better,\" \"time heals everything.\" but it doesn't feel like it's gonna get better. it feels like the world just stopped. everything is just empty and gray. i feel like i'm just existing in this huge hole and there's no point to any of it anymore. it's just constant pain.",
